_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2020-07-03T14:39:24Z","updated_at":"2020-07-03T14:39:24Z","author_association":"OWNER","body":"Ah wait, so in that screenshot you had `legacy_windows=False` ? \r\n\r\nRich subtracts 1 from the terminal width on legacy windows. This is because a new line character at the end of the line is treated as having a width of 1 and wraps the line (on other terminals it is treated as 0 width).\r\n\r\nIf you really really want all the box options, setting `safe_box=True` is your only option at the moment.","performed_via_github_app":null},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/willmcgugan/rich/issues/comments/653578384","html_url":"https://github.com/willmcgugan/rich/issues/135#issuecomment-653578384","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/willmcgugan/rich/issues/135","id":653578384,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDY1MzU3ODM4NA==","user":{"login":"Niraj-Kamdar","id":51387861,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjUxMzg3ODYx","avatar_url":"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/51387861?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar","html_url":"https://github.com/Niraj-Kamdar","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2020-07-03T14:39:40Z","updated_at":"2020-07-03T14:39:40Z","author_association":"NONE","body":"Yes both looks same width.\r\n```console\r\n══════════════════════════════════════════════════\r\nWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWW\r\n```","performed_via_github_app":null},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/willmcgugan/rich/issues/comments/653593666","html_url":"https://github.com/willmcgugan/rich/issues/135#issuecomment-653593666","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/willmcgugan/rich/issues/135","id":653593666,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDY1MzU5MzY2Ng==","user":{"login":"Niraj-Kamdar","id":51387861,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjUxMzg3ODYx","avatar_url":"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/51387861?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar","html_url":"https://github.com/Niraj-Kamdar","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2020-07-03T15:19:40Z","updated_at":"2020-07-03T15:19:40Z","author_association":"NONE","body":"> I guess there can be some registry value that stores which font is being set as default for console.\r\n\r\n I have found registry path that stores current console fonts of current user: `Computer\\HKEY_CURRENT_USER\\Console`\r\nFor cmd it is under: `Computer\\HKEY_CURRENT_USER\\Console\\%SystemRoot%_System32_cmd.exe`\r\nand \r\nFor powershell 32bit it is under: `Computer\\HKEY_CURRENT_USER\\Console\\%SystemRoot%_System32_WindowsPowerShell_v1.0_powershell.exe`\r\nFor powershell 64 bit it is under:\r\n`Computer\\HKEY_CURRENT_USER\\Console\\%SystemRoot%_SysWOW64_WindowsPowerShell_v1.0_powershell.exe`\r\nHere, fontface contains name of the font and there is also some meta data about fonts under this registry path.\r\nIf somehow we can know current terminal is powershell or cmd and font set is truetype or raster than we can surely tell that texts is going to render or not.","performed_via_github_app":null},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/willmcgugan/rich/issues/comments/653604173","html_url":"https://github.com/willmcgugan/rich/issues/135#issuecomment-653604173","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/willmcgugan/rich/issues/135","id":653604173,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDY1MzYwNDE3Mw==","user":{"login":"willmcgugan","id":554369,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjU1NDM2OQ==","avatar_url":"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/554369?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan","html_url":"https://github.com/willmcgugan","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2020-07-03T15:49:19Z","updated_at":"2020-07-03T15:49:19Z","author_association":"OWNER","body":"> If somehow we can know current terminal is powershell or cmd and font set is truetype or raster than we can surely tell that texts is going to render or not.\r\n\r\nIt would require knowing in advance which fonts render and which don't. You might be right most of the time, until you find one user who installs a custom raster font. I also suspect that those registry keys aren't guaranteed to be the same in the future (v1.0 is a clear indication of that).\r\n\r\nSince you can't know with 100% confidence, I think it is safer to disable by default. ","performed_via_github_app":null},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/willmcgugan/rich/issues/comments/653604459","html_url":"https://github.com/willmcgugan/rich/issues/135#issuecomment-653604459","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/willmcgugan/rich/issues/135","id":653604459,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDY1MzYwNDQ1OQ==","user":{"login":"Niraj-Kamdar","id":51387861,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjUxMzg3ODYx","avatar_url":"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/51387861?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar","html_url":"https://github.com/Niraj-Kamdar","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Niraj-Kamdar/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2020-07-03T15:50:19Z","updated_at":"2020-07-03T15:50:19Z","author_association":"NONE","body":"> Ah wait, so in that screenshot you had `legacy_windows=False` ?\r\n> \r\n> Rich subtracts 1 from the terminal width on legacy windows. This is because a new line character at the 